byline.original: Correspondence of The New-York Daily Times

lead_paragraph: The Westchester County Agricultural and Horticultural Fair opened to-day at this place with a prospect of being the best ever held in the County. The show of cattle is said to exceed, in some of the varieties, the State Fair at Rochester, and the contributors are pouring in from all directions.

headline.main: Fair of the Westchester Agricultural Society.
